response.overview: STARDOM live in Tokyo, Japan on March 15th, 2025 with the final day of the Cinderella Tournament 2025. Matches featuring • Fukigen Death vs. Rian • Empress Nexus Venus (HANAKO, Maika & Waka Tsukiyama) vs. Akira Kurogane, Tabata & Yuria Hime • Semi Final: Azusa Inaba vs. Sayaka Kurara • Semi Final: Hanan vs. Rina • Neo Genesis (AZM, Mei Seira, Miyu Amasaki & Suzu Suzuki) vs. HATE (Momo Watanabe, Natsuko Tora, Ruaka & Saya Kamitani) • STARS (Hazuki, Koguma, Mayu Iwatani, Momo Kohgo & Saya Iida) vs. God's Eye (Lady C, Ranna Yagami, Saki Kashima, Syuri & Tomoka Inaba) • Saori Anou & Tam Nakano vs. Cosmic Angels (Aya Sakura & Yuna Mizumori) • Mina Shirakawa vs. Thekla • Cinderella Tournament 2025 Final Match • Wonder Of Stardom Title Match: Starlight Kid (c) vs. Konami
response.title: STARDOM Cinderella Tournament 2025 • Finals
